The '''''Diva Book of Short Stories''''' and its successor ''Groundswell: The Second Diva Book of Short Stories'' are [[anthology|anthologies]]  of [[fiction]]al [[short story|short stories]] about [[lesbian]], [[gay]], [[bisexual]], and [[transgender]] people.  

The ''Diva Book of Short Stories'', [[editing|edited]] by Helen Sandler, was the first book in the series.  It was [[literary criticism|critically]] well-received, winning the [[2002 Lambda Literary Awards|2002 Lambda Literary Award]] for fictional anthology.

